  "overview_en": "The 'Cambridge Summit' Academic Summer Camp is a 16-day program designed for students aged 13 to 18 eager to experience life at a world-leading university. Hosted at the University of Cambridge, this program combines rigorous academic courses, hands-on workshops, and cultural immersion experiences. Participants will engage with Cambridge professors, explore cutting-edge topics in artificial intelligence, business, sociology, and computer science, and gain valuable insights into university life and career planning. Focused on academic excellence and personal growth, this program serves as a bridge to Ivy League schools and beyond.",
  "overview_zh": "'剑桥峰会'学术夏令营是一个为期16天的项目，专为13至18岁、渴望体验世界顶尖大学生活的学生设计。该项目在剑桥大学举办，结合了严谨的学术课程、实践工作坊和文化沉浸体验。参与者将与剑桥大学教授互动，探索人工智能、商业、社会学和计算机科学等领域的前沿话题，并获得关于大学生活和职业规划的宝贵见解。该项目注重学术卓越与个人成长，是通往常春藤盟校及更广阔天地的桥梁。",
  "highlights_en": "Cambridge University Faculty: Learn directly from University of Cambridge staff renowned for their expertise and groundbreaking research.\n\nPersonalized Academic Mentorship: Receive one-on-one guidance and essay feedback to enhance your academic profile.\n\nOfficial Certification: Earn a completion certificate and personalized reference letter from Cambridge professors.\n\nElite Scholarship: Outstanding participants may receive a £500 scholarship.\n\nCultural Immersion: Experience Cambridge life with punting on the River Cam, formal dinners, and tours of Oxford and London.\n\nSmall Class Sizes: Limited to 99 students per session, ensuring personalized attention and a supportive learning environment.",
  "highlights_zh": "剑桥大学教授：直接向剑桥大学教职员工学习，他们以其专业知识和开创性研究而闻名。\n\n个性化学术指导：获得一对一的导师指导和论文反馈，提升学术背景。\n\n官方认证：获得剑桥大学教授颁发的结业证书及个性化推荐信。\n\n精英奖学金：优秀参与者有机会获得500英镑奖学金。\n\n文化沉浸：体验剑桥生活，包括康河撑船、正式晚宴以及牛津和伦敦的游览。\n\n小班教学：每期课程限99名学生，确保个性化关注和支持性学习环境。",
  "itinerary_en": "[Cambridge University Summer Program Itinerary]\n\n<h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold mb-3\">16-Day Detailed Schedule</h3>\n<table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr class=\"bg-gray-100\">\n      <th class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Day</th>\n      <th class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Activities</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 1: Morning</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Airport pickup, gather at Cambridge University College, distribute room keys</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 1: Afternoon</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Familiarize with living environment</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 1: Evening</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Dinner</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 2: Morning</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Lesson 1</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 2: Afternoon</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Cambridge Walking Exploration</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 2: Evening</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Welcome Ceremony</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 3: Morning</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Lesson 2</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 3: Afternoon</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">Punting on the River Cam (Xu Zhimo style)</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">Day 3: Evening</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2