>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十天: 下午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">课后工作坊</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十天: 晚上</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">迷你运动会</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十一天: 上午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">课程8</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十一天: 下午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">参观卡文迪许实验室</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十一天: 晚上</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">剑桥学长分享会</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十二天: 上午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">课程9</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十二天: 下午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">课后工作坊</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十二天: 晚上</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">正式晚宴</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十三天: 上午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">课程10</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十三天: 下午</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">毕业论文答辩</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十三天: 晚上</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">结营仪式</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十四天: 全天</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">牛津之旅</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2 font-medium\">第十五天</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">欢送离营，专车送机</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">第十六天</td>\n      <td class=\"border border-gray-300 p-2\">安全抵达国内</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>",
  "features_en": "Accommodation: Stay in Cambridge University student dormitories for an authentic campus experience.\n\nDining: Enjoy traditional British meals and formal dining experiences, including Harry Potter-style formal dinners.\n\nActivities: Blend of academic courses, workshops, and extracurriculars like punting, debates, and sports.\n\nSafety: 24-hour supervision by experienced staff throughout the program.\n\nCertification: Receive an official certificate and personalized reference letter from Cambridge University professors.",
  "features_zh": "住宿：入住剑桥大学学生宿舍，体验真实的大学校园生活。\n\n餐饮：享用传统英式餐点及正式晚宴体验，包括哈利波特风格的正式晚宴。\n\n活动：结合学术课程、工作坊以及课外活动，如撑船、辩论和体育运动。\n\n安全：全程监护，由经验丰富的工作人员提供24小时支持。\n\n认证：获得剑桥大学教授颁发的官方证书及个性化推荐信。",
